---
type: structured
description: Context data for prose review (paired with review.system.j2)
---
{# Variables: age_range, location, characters, concept, beats, previous_checklist, current_iteration #}

{% block base_instruction %}
Target audience age range: {{ age_range }}

Story Elements (use these to validate character names in the outputs):
{
    location: {{ location }},
    characters: {{ characters }},
}

Director's Concept (the vision this prose should follow):
{{ concept }}

Story Beats (the beats this prose expands):
{{ beats }}

Previous Checklist (completed=true items are past decisions - DO NOT reverse them):
{{ previous_checklist }}

Current Iteration: {{ current_iteration }}

CHECKLIST INSTRUCTIONS:
- For each previous checklist item, evaluate if the issue has been FIXED in the current version.
- If an issue is now fixed, include it in your response with completed=true and completed_at_iteration={{ current_iteration }}.
- If an issue is NOT fixed, include it with completed=false and completed_at_iteration=null.
- Add any NEW issues discovered to the checklist (with completed=false and completed_at_iteration=null).
- Keep ALL items (both completed and incomplete) in your final checklist for tracking.
{% endblock %}
